Description:
You arrive at a large tree that appears to be an owl sanctuary. As you approach the elf guarding the place says to you:

"Ohh! what a good timing... I really need your help. The intense cold is agitating the owls... we usually sing them an ancient song among several of us to calm them down, but the other elves are busy with the owl guardians.

I can teach you that ancient song and even give you some magic shards if you help me calm them down."
DescriptionAction: Do you want to learn and sing the ancient song?
